Quote: <i>Pig&#769;.face&#769;.</i> (p&ibreve.g&#769;.f&amacr.s&#769;.), <i>n.; pl. PIGFACES. } </i>(Bot.) <i>The Pig's&#769;. face&#769;.</i> (p&ibreve.gz&#769;.-); pl. PIGS' FACES. } fruit of the Australian ice plant (<i>Mesembryanthemum sequilaterale</i>) : - called also <i>canajong</i>. In form it resembles a pig's head and face.
